{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1661793184.1891005", "card_id": "Q_550575935", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 369}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "河南警方称村镇银行案已逮捕 234 人，侦办工作正纵深推进，为何会发生此类现象？如何从法律角度解读？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据平安许昌： 经我市公安机关进一步侦查发现：以犯罪嫌疑人吕奕为首的犯罪团伙非法控制禹州新民生等 4 家村镇银行, 涉嫌实施系列严重犯罪。该犯罪团伙在正常存款利息之外，用非法获取的部分资金，以年化收益率 13%-18%「 贴息 」 标准为诱饵吸揽资金，该 「 贴息 」 经资金掮客层层 盘剥后，被部分大额资金客户获取。 目前，公安机关已抓获一大批犯罪嫌疑人，其中已逮捕 234 人，追赃挽损工作取得重大进展。案件侦办工作正在依法纵深推进。 来源：平安许昌"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-e9cb965e6f8d664408c580ced36336d7_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "1239 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/550575935"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I053msrv40J0dEAMaCDg0NjMzOTk5IIGIspgGMEw40AlAAHIJNTUwNTc1OTM1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1661793184.1903818", "card_id": "Q_550516766", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 405}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "8 月 29 日离岸人民币兑美元跌破 6.92 关口，哪些因素导致的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "每经 AI 快讯，8 月 29 日，离岸人民币兑美元连续跌破 6.90 、 6.91 、 6.92 三道关口，日内跌超 300 点。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b82cb8e2058635459610490f1397e23c_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "730 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/550516766"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I053msrv40J0dEAMaCDg0NjIwODQ2IIDOsJgGME443AtAAXIJNTUwNTE2NzY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1661793184.1914654", "card_id": "Q_550419411", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 106}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "8 月 28 日成都进入公共场所须查验 48 小时核酸，目前成都疫情形势如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "【#成都进入公共场所须查验 48 小时核酸#】发布会上通报，为进一步降低疫